      <title>报纸称，加拿大监管机构将限制高负债借款人的抵押贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/canada-banking-regulator-cap-mortgages-highly-indebted-borrowers-newspaper-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《环球邮报》周五报道，加拿大银行监管机构正在限制银行住宅抵押贷款组合中的高杠杆贷款数量，这些贷款随着房价的上涨而飙升，使加拿大借款人成为世界上负债最重的国家之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/canada-banking-regulator-cap-mortgages-highly-indebted-borrowers-newspaper-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 16:36:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
