      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/maersk-will-avoid-red-sea-despite-eu-security-operation-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马士基航运公司周五表示，尽管欧盟采取了提高该地区安全的举措，但由于风险水平持续升高，恢复红海航行还为时过早。]]></description>
